text: Jože Zidar (7 September 1927 - 25 December 2012) was a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2012 deaths Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Yugoslavia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Jesenice, Jesenice
